context_meta.summary: In a rare coming-together of IT cognoscenti, India and Taiwan are collaborating in organising the global ICT and Internet of Things (IoT) show Computex 2018 and the Smart Asia trade expo here from Wednesday. context_meta.summary: Patna: Indian Institute of Technology (IIT)-Patna director Pushpak Bhattacharyya has been appointed chairman of the committee for standardisation in artificial intelligence set up by the Bureau of Indian Standards under the ministry of consumer affairs.
